<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=8391&amp;p=35800#p35800"><![CDATA[
I was able to get it to work with these settings:<br />Click twice on Games then select Custom from drop down list then right-click and Edit item.<br /><br />Command is empty<br /><br />Link: C:\ProgramData\Microsoft\Windows\Start Menu\Programs\Games<br /><br />Label: Games<br /><br />Tip: $Menu.GamesTip<br /><br />Icon: %SystemRoot%\System32\imageres.dll, 14<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=32372">dfm0</a> — Mon May 07, 2018 1:26 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
